Node.Notes: Word new moon also means month. Hebrew calendar based on a lunar month that began with every new moon.
Uncertain. Tree assumes the logic to be: if they obey, they will be special as opposed to just part of Yahweh’s normal possession (parenthetical explanation: for all the earth belongs to Yahweh).
The exact meaning of a kingdom of priests is uncertain. The basic idea of God's people as priests seems clear (which the New Testament also expresses, e.g., 1pe2:5,9; rev1:6; 5:10; and 20:6).
